column11: Metadata:  Measured biomass 2 weeks after planting by harvesting 3 x 12" rows in the northeast corner of each plot.  (Avoiding the overlapped planting area).  Cut to ground level.  Also counted the number of each plants within each harvested row.  Also took plant counts but did not harvest those same quadrat areas for the intercrop plots (IWG/crop).  Also came back and did plant counts (same 3x12") of the best IWG mon stretches- since those plots have very poor establishment.
